snippet.title: WonderSwan Color - From TV Animation One Piece - Chopper no Daibouken © 2003 Bandai - Gameplay

DESCRIPTION
One Piece: Chopper no Daibouken is a Role-Playing game, developed by TOSE and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 2003.
